        {
            "name": "Drow Rogue",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Loners at heart, drow rogues trust no one\u2014least of all fellow slayers. These drow rely on awareness and adaptation to survive the cutthroat nature of their society.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Humanoid</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"14\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Society</a></u>)</b>: DC 16",
